ps://ref.ly/Lev13:8\">LEV 13:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:10\">LEV 13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:11\">LEV 13:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:12\">LEV 13:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:12\">LEV 13:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:18\">LEV 13:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:20\">LEV 13:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:21\">LEV 13:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:22\">LEV 13:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:24\">LEV 13:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:25\">LEV 13:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:26\">LEV 13:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:27\">LEV 13:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:28\">LEV 13:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:30\">LEV 13:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:31\">LEV 13:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:32\">LEV 13:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:34\">LEV 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:34\">LEV 13:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:35\">LEV 13:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:36\">LEV 13:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:38\">LEV 13:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:39\">LEV 13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:39\">LEV 13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:43\">LEV 13:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:48\">LEV 13:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:48\">LEV 13:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:49\">LEV 13:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:49\">LEV 13:49</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:51\">LEV 13:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:51\">LEV 13:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:52\">LEV 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:53\">LEV 13:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:56\">LEV 13:56</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:57\">LEV 13:57</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:58\">LEV 13:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev13:59\">LEV 13:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:17\">LEV 15:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:27\">LEV 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:6\">NUM 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:8\">NUM 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:10\">NUM 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:11\">NUM 4:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:12\">NUM 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num4:14\">NUM 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:5\">NUM 19:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:20\">NUM 31:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:8\">2KI 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:4\">JOB 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:4\">JOB 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:5\">JOB 7:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:11\">JOB 10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job18:13\">JOB 18:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:20\">JOB 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:20\">JOB 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:26\">JOB 19:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:30\">JOB 30:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job40:31\">JOB 40:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:23\">JER 13:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:4\">LAM 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:8\">LAM 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam5:10\">LAM 5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:6\">EZK 37:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:8\">EZK 37:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:2\">MIC 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:3\">MIC 3:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：תַּחַשׁ</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：tachash)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:10\">EZK 16:10</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：βυρσεύς</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：burseus)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:43\">ACT 9:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:6\">ACT 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:32\">ACT 10:32</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：δερμάτινος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：dermatinos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:4\">MAT 3:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:6\">MRK 1:6</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0377_tanner_with_leather.jpg\" alt=\"制革匠在加工皮革\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">制革匠在加工皮革 (Deutsche Fotothek, Public domain, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>皮革是按照特殊工艺来处理的动物皮，目的是去除皮上的毛和防止皮革腐烂或变脆。制作皮革的人称为皮匠或硝皮匠。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>皮革有很多用途，包括制作皮带和凉鞋等服饰，做成装水和葡萄酒等液体的容器，有时也用来制作牲畜的挽具和其他绳索。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>有些语言会有一个专门表示“皮革”的词语，但许多语言会使用与动物的“皮”相同的词。</p>\n<p>希伯来文<em>tachash</em> 指的是水生动物儒艮（参<em>All Creatures Great and Small</em> ，第42—43页）。圣经只在提到儒艮皮的时候才提到这种动物，所以它通常与希伯来文<em>‘or</em> 同时出现。<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:10\">EZK 16:10</a> 省略了<em>‘or</em> ，但是<em>tachash</em> 在该处表示用这种动物的皮制成的精鞣皮革。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
